title: Horobo
description: Horobo is a Human interactive robot design contest, where you can make use of basic sensors and electronics and build a feedback control system of any bodily movement.
rules: A team can contain at most 3 members more than that can't be encouraged.
Must be present at the allocated area when your called no delays in presentation will be encouraged.
Participants must explain their innovation within 5 mins.
